      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEATON (2) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 29.69 beating Good Luck Babe. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can continue on his winning ways. PROMISES MADE (8) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at Hobart (19.46) last time and making it two straight wins. Solid record here winning seven races. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. ALVESTON (5) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at this track over 515m behind Bradmore (30.38) in a Special conditions race. Has the ability to give this a shake. MOLLY POTION (4) cannot be ruled out.",
